search.postprocess:
| dedup id
| rename "title_multiloc.en-GB" AS Title, dislikes_count AS Dislikes, likes_count AS Likes, overall_score AS OverallScore, comments_count AS Comments
| rename slug AS _slug
| eventstats max(Dislikes) AS max_dislikes, max(Likes) AS max_likes, max(Comments) as max_comments, max(OverallScore) as max_score
| eval isMaxLikes=IF(max_likes==Likes,Title." (".Likes.")",null())
| eval isMaxDisLikes=IF(max_dislikes==Dislikes,Title." (".Dislikes.")",null())
| eval isMaxComments=IF(max_comments==Comments,Title." (".Comments.")",null())
| eval isMaxScore=IF(max_score==OverallScore,Title." (".OverallScore.")",null())
| stats ,latest(isMaxLikes) AS maxLiked, latest(isMaxDisLikes) AS maxDisliked, latest(isMaxComments) AS maxCommented, latest(isMaxScore) AS maxScored

index=github action=created release.id=* | rename release.* as *

index=github NOT "check_run.conclusion"="null" NOT "workflow_run.conclusion"="null" NOT TERM("workflow_job") (action IN ("opened","created","completed", "closed") OR NOT action=*)
| eval type=IF(LIKE(number,"%"),"pullrequest","other")
| eval {type}_action=action
| eval repo=coalesce('repository.full_name',json_extract(_raw,"repository.full_name"), json_extract(_raw, "pull_request.base.repo.full_name")) 
| eval a_pullrequest_id=coalesce('workflow_run.pull_requests{}.id','pull_request.id','check_run.pull_requests{}.id') 
| eval a_checkrun_id=json_extract(_raw, "check_run.id") 
| eval a_workflow_run='workflow_run.id' 
| eval workflow_status='workflow_run.conclusion' 
| eval workflow_name='workflow_run.name' 
| eval checkrun_status='check_run.conclusion' 
| eval checkrun_name='check_run.name' 
| eval job_{checkrun_name}=checkrun_status
| stats values(pull_request.title) AS Title, values(pull_request.user.login) AS User, latest(job_*) AS job_*, values(pull_request.html_url) as url, latest(pullrequest_action) as latestAction values(pullrequest_action) as actions values(a_workflow_run) AS workflow_id, values(a_checkrun_id) AS workflow_jobs, latest(workflow_status) AS workflow_status, values(workflow_name) AS workflow_name, values(checkrun_status) AS checkrun_status, values(checkrun_name) as checkrun_name by a_pullrequest_id, repo 
| eval workflow=mvzip(workflow_name, workflow_status, " = ") 
| eval checkruns=mvzip(checkrun_name, checkrun_status, " = ")
| fields - *_name *_status workflow_* checkruns
| search actions!=closed
| table a_pullrequest_id repo User Title url actions workflow job_*
| rename a_pullrequest_id AS PullRequestID

index=github number=* 
| eval repo=json_extract(_raw, "pull_request.base.repo.full_name")
| stats latest(action) as latestAction values(action) as actions latest(pull_request.html_url) as url by number, repo, pull_request.title, pull_request.user.login, pull_request.id
| search actions!=closed
| fields - latestAction actions
| rename number AS "PR#", repo AS Repo, pull_request.title AS "Pull Request Title", pull_request.user.login AS User
